text: Novyye Bishindy () is a rural locality (a selo) in Verkhnebishindinsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 274 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Tuymazy, 3 km from Verkhniye Bishindy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Novyye Bishindy
